WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.989
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.989 --> 00:00:04.800
Well, we see the rat in the White House.

00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:12.765
