00:00:35.657 --> 00:00:37.080
' And I warned you all.

00:00:37.080 --> 00:00:38.925
I said, 'This man is very dark.

00:00:38.925 --> 00:00:41.337
I see satanic origins behind him.

00:00:41.337 --> 00:00:42.526
There's very dark things.

00:00:42.526 --> 00:00:51.239
