But it's like a hybrid.

00:01:02.444 --> 00:01:05.351
He has hybrid thinking.

00:01:06.864 --> 00:01:13.404
That's just the way I saw it in the spirit, that this was a mind that was hybrid.

00:01:13.404 --> 00:01:19.160
I don't know if he is a hybrid; I just know that there's something about this man.

00:01:19.160 --> 00:01:22.017
He thinks in a way that is not normal.

00:01:22.017 --> 00:01:27.250
And all of a sudden, now he's the cheerleader for freedom of speech.

00:01:27.940 --> 00:01:32.446
And so all these people are liking him, and he's like, 'I'm your buddy.

00:01:32.446 --> 00:01:33.371
I'm your pal.

00:01:33.371 --> 00:01:34.034
Follow me.

00:01:34.034 --> 00:01:37.609
