00:01:48.479 --> 00:01:48.822
Okay?

00:01:55.359 --> 00:01:56.559
And it had humongous, not little bitty horns, huge horns that looked like huge horns.

00:02:07.884 --> 00:02:08.276
And I heard Nephilim as I saw a rat again.

00:02:21.707 --> 00:02:24.160
I just saw a rat.

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:26.965
When I closed my eyes again, I saw a rat.

00:02:26.965 --> 00:02:33.606
But this time, the rat had a black face, a white body, and a black tail, a black back end.

00:02:33.606 --> 00:02:38.497
White in the middle, black on the ends.

00:02:38.497 --> 00:02:49.233
And that's what he's looking at, and it had a light shining on it, like a spotlight.

00:02:49.233 --> 00:03:02.879
I saw a spotlight on this rat, and it was shining as it was trying to crawl through the night.

00:03:02.879 --> 00:03:12.782
As it was trying to crawl through the night, there was a spotlight on it, exposing where it was.

00:03:14.346 --> 00:03:17.987
I believe an exposing of darkness is happening as we pray, an exposing of the rats within.

00:03:17.987 --> 00:03:21.188
Exposing of the rats within, such that there will be embarrassing moments for politicians.

00:03:22.103 --> 00:03:24.103
But not only that—justice, justice, justice, justice in Jesus' name.

00:03:24.103 --> 00:03:28.060
Thank you, Father, that all hidden things be revealed concerning these things.

00:03:39.440 --> 00:03:39.760
I am praying for the president because the Lord revealed to me there was a rat in the White House, and so I have been praying over that.

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:42.570
And whenever Elon Musk...

00:03:42.570 --> 00:03:56.743
there's things I know everybody likes Elon Musk and they say he's on the train, we're excited about Elon Musk, but I'm telling you I've seen some very dark things, and the Lord has warned me about this man.

00:04:03.599 --> 00:04:06.492
