00:06:34.868 --> 00:06:48.200
Elon Musk came out today, as many of you may not know, and said that the reason why President Trump has not released the Epstein files is because he's in the Epstein files and says he should be impeached.

00:06:48.200 --> 00:06:56.693
There are all these things he's agreeing with, saying that President Trump should be removed, that he has evidence that President Trump has been messing around doing bad things, right?

00:06:57.120 --> 00:06:58.171
So the rat is now...

00:07:00.210 --> 00:07:03.507
and, you know, when you're seeing a rat in the spirit, you're like, 'What is this rat, Lord?

00:07:05.440 --> 00:07:06.453
What are you showing me a rat?

00:07:06.453 --> 00:07:08.969
' A rat is a narc.

00:07:15.912 --> 00:07:16.176
A rat is somebody who infiltrates and is sneaky.

00:07:16.176 --> 00:07:17.231
Rats are sneaky.

00:07:17.231 --> 00:07:22.880
So the Lord showed me this man is sneaky; he's in there, and he is not a true friend.

00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:26.560
And I saw things that were tied to him to Russia.

00:07:36.680 --> 00:07:37.240
And I can't go into the depth of that for my own safety, but I'm just telling you all I knew by the spirit of God to warn you.

00:07:37.240 --> 00:07:41.462
Even when there's so many Christians who are like, 'Oh, I'm on the Elon train.

00:07:41.462 --> 00:07:42.513
He's so nice.

00:07:42.513 --> 00:07:47.480
He's giving millions of dollars trying to help Donald Trump.

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:51.268
