00:08:28.380 --> 00:08:29.400
We're friends.

00:08:29.400 --> 00:08:33.439
We'll talk behind closed doors,' and you confide things.

00:08:45.880 --> 00:08:46.270
What things will be brought out to the surface in the confiding because this didn't happen the way he thought?

00:08:47.440 --> 00:08:51.030
The whole budget deal of the $5 trillion and all this was just upsetting him.

00:08:52.288 --> 00:08:57.469
You know, 'Well, you're DOGE and we helped you out,' and all the corruption in the government.

