00:09:46.994 --> 00:09:52.410
God's a God of justice, and God is watching all of it.

00:09:58.853 --> 00:09:59.058
And there'll be an exposing of things in the days ahead.

00:10:11.623 --> 00:10:12.006
There'll be exposing of your past in some circumstances where it looks like it tries to come back.

00:10:12.006 --> 00:10:16.853
Well, it bites you because you think, 'Well, I'm too powerful to be touched.

00:10:23.956 --> 00:10:24.231
I have so much money, I can't be touched.

00:10:24.231 --> 00:10:33.040
' And yet, what happens is the pride, and the devil hangs you with your own rope.

00:10:33.040 --> 00:10:34.280
Do you see?

00:10:34.280 --> 00:10:40.753
But God is a God of justice, and I told you there'll be a shaking in politics.

00:10:40.753 --> 00:10:42.893
Remember that.

00:10:42.893 --> 00:10:54.259
There'll be a shaking in politics, there'll be a shaking in the church, there'll be a shaking in the earth's crust, there'll be a shaking in the finances in the days ahead.

