00:12:47.226 --> 00:12:52.559
Great judgment and trial is whenever you're separated from God for eternity.

00:12:52.559 --> 00:12:59.246
True judgment from the Lord is separation for eternity, that you would burn in hell for eternity.

00:12:59.246 --> 00:13:11.200
That is the most important thing that you make your decision on: either you choose Jesus today as your Lord and personal Savior, or you're choosing hell.

00:13:11.200 --> 00:13:12.499
There is no in-between.

00:13:12.499 --> 00:13:15.337
You're either hot or you're cold.

00:13:20.820 --> 00:13:22.189
If you're lukewarm, he said he'd spew you out of his mouth like you taste coffee.

