00:15:43.440 --> 00:15:50.186
This is the most important thing on the Father's heart: to bring in the lost, to bring in the unsaved.

00:15:58.240 --> 00:15:58.560
" And I thought, well, let's do it.

00:15:58.560 --> 00:16:05.739
